{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"222545-chhotta-hati-jol-khete-shikhla","title":"ছোট হাতি জল খেতে শিখল","description":"ছোট হাতি জল পান করার চেষ্টা করল. সে জল পান করার জন্য কী কী করল? কাহিনিটি পড়ে দেখো. ","language":"Bengali","langCode":"bn","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Pratham Content Group (West Bengal)"],"illustrators":["Partho Sengupta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Education Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/222545-chhotta-hati-jol-khete-shikhla"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/283163/size3/37a6f82e0194f64250d9d781c5ca07eb.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/283163/size6/37a6f82e0194f64250d9d781c5ca07eb.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279032/size6/2a05410559e907f0651209b6fccd465d.jpg","text":"একটা ছিল ছোট হাতি। \nবনে বাদাড়ে ঘুরে বেড়ায়। \nঘুরতে ঘুরতে তার  তেষ্টা পেয়ে গেল।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279034/size6/035d96023358f1c7258ad2a602db2704.jpg","text":"এখন কি করি? যায় নদীর কাছে। \nনদীতে অনেক জল। জল খাবে কি করে?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279035/size6/ad3e9902e3496e018151b87c24bb22d3.jpg","text":"দেখি তো কান ডুবিয়ে। \nনা, তাতে তো জল উঠল না।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279036/size6/f8cc3e29a92544e3ce456ed57d051c5b.jpg","text":"এবার দেখি লেজ ডুবিয়ে। \nতাতেও জল খেতে পারল না।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279038/size6/1dd1a6deade28447e2909b50a1ac2d54.jpg","text":"এমন সময় ওখানে এল মা হাতি।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279041/size6/937672078519b529afe4a8398a6b5b11.jpg","text":"মা গেল ছোট হাতির কাছে।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279055/size6/f31d99cc52092828d257c50daf0e59bf.jpg","text":"সে তার ছানার শুঁড় ধরে জলে ডুবিয়ে দিল।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/279050/size6/845f950b358f4e5dde857982b4f8765b.jpg","text":"হাতির ছানা চোঁ\nচোঁ করে জল খেতে লাগল।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":73}}